Exercise 14.21: Write the Sales_data operators so that + does the actual
addition and += calls +. Discuss the disadvantages of this approach compared
to the way these operators were defined in § 14.3 (p. 560) and § 14.4 (p.
564).

Answer:
Sales_data Sales_data::operator+(const Sales_data& other)
{
    Sales_data sum;
    sum.units_sold = sum.units_sold + other.units_sold;
    sum.revenue = sum.revenue + other.revenue;
    return sum;
}

Sales_data Sales_data::operator+=(const Sales_data& other)
{
    Sales_data sum = *this;
    sum = *this + other;
    return *this;
}

